{"word":"G584 - ἀποδείκνυμι - apodeíknymi - ap-od-ike'-noo-mee - Prove","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποδείκνυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apodeíknymi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-od-ike'-noo-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Prove</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இரட்சிக்கப்படு, ரூபி, காண்பி, ஒப்புக்கொடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to point away from oneself, to point out, show forth; to expose to view, exhibit"},{"paragraph":"2. to declare"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G1166 - δεικνύω - deiknýō - dike-noo'-o/1166\">G1166</a>; to <i>show off</i>, that is, <i>exhibit</i>; figuratively to <i>demonstrate</i>, that is, <i>accredit:</i> - (ap-) prove, set forth, shew.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}